info.help_text:
This report gives information about GTP-C v2 create session response messages received per cause code on S5 interface (SGW <- PGW).
Use case specific instructions:
- This report can be used to troubleshoot the 'Create Session Request sent on S5 interface' messages;
- Note, 'Ratio' column is applicable on GV25 level only.
